<.dm_breadcrumb class="px-4">
  <:crumb to={~p"/art-component"}>Art Components</:crumb>
  <:crumb>Gemini Input</:crumb>
</.dm_breadcrumb>

<.dm_card class="w-full h-full overflow-auto" body_class="p-4">
  <:title class="flex flex-row justify-center items-center gap-3">
    <span class="text-4xl text-primary">Gemini Input</span>
    <span class="text-sm opacity-60">dm_art_gemini_input</span>
  </:title>

  <.dm_markdown content={"""
  ## Overview
  Gemini-style animated gradient input using the `<el-dm-art-gemini-input>` custom element.
  The border uses a rotating conic-gradient with CSS Houdini `@property` for smooth animation.

  ## Usage
  ```elixir
  <!-- Default -->
  <.dm_art_gemini_input id="gemini" />

  <!-- Small -->
  <.dm_art_gemini_input id="gemini-sm" size="sm" />

  <!-- Large with custom placeholder -->
  <.dm_art_gemini_input id="gemini-lg" size="lg" placeholder="Search or ask anything..." />
  ```
  """} />

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Default (md)</h3>
  <div class="flex justify-center p-8 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
    <.dm_art_gemini_input id="gemini-demo-default" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Small</h3>
  <div class="flex justify-center p-8 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
    <.dm_art_gemini_input id="gemini-demo-sm" size="sm" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Large</h3>
  <div class="flex justify-center p-8 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
    <.dm_art_gemini_input id="gemini-demo-lg" size="lg" />
  </div>

  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Custom Placeholder</h3>
  <div class="flex justify-center p-8 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
    <.dm_art_gemini_input id="gemini-demo-placeholder" placeholder="Search or ask anything..." />
  </div>
</.dm_card>
